Body: Description: We are ready to migrate from StealthAudit to Enterprise Auditor and would like assistance with the upgrade process. We will be migrating it from a 2012 server to a new 2022 server.
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Scottie Taylor, Tony Do

What We've Learned Updated: Today we:

Discussed the process of migrating the StealthAudit console to a new application server. This will start with a pre-fight process in preparation for the official migration.

Next Steps Updated: Our next steps are:

To schedule a meeting to perform the pre-flight process.
